-------------------------------------------------------------------
 Contents
-------------------------------------------------------------------

The package comprises these functions

式成式 demo.m			: Compare LDR to the other CE algorithms
 戍式 135069.jpg		: test image for demo.m
 戍式 yuv2rgb.m		: convert yuv to rgb
 戍式 rgb2yuv.m		: convert rgb to yuv
 戍式 QM				: Quality metric
 戌式成式 CE (directory)
   戍式 HE.m			: Histogram Equalization
   戍式 WAHE.m		: Weighted Approximated Histogram Equalization
   戍式 CVC.m			: Contextual and Variational Contrast enhancement
   戌式 LDR.m			: Layered Difference Representation [1]


-------------------------------------------------------------------
 Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------

式 Unzip LDR.zip
式 Run demo.m


-------------------------------------------------------------------
 Requirements
-------------------------------------------------------------------

式 Matlab v.7.1 or later with installed:
  -- Image Processing Toolbox


